    "7904501": {
        "Desc": "Listen to the announcement",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Park Announcement Speaker",
                    "T": "Staff and equipment in position. Mechanisms are prepped and ready."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Park Announcement Speaker",
                    "T": "This performance of \"The Black Nacre and the All-Devouring Kraken,\" a play from \"Daiya's Three-Day Reverie,\" will now begin!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Narrator On Speaker",
                    "T": "Docked in the port closest to the rumored location of the treasure, the crew of the pirate ship \"Black Nacre\" is recruiting new sailors and restocking before the final and most crucial leg of the voyage..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Narrator On Speaker",
                    "T": "Experienced adventurers set foot on the deck of the Black Nacre. They're outstanding fighters, but novice sailors..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chief Mate",
                    "T": "Ahoy there, landlubbers! Get on over here!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? The voice from the speaker changed. It sounds like someone really serious is calling us..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So, it's trying to interact with us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chief Mate",
                    "T": "Who else would I be talking to? You're the best out of this sorry bunch of scallywags, we can't set sail without you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chief Mate",
                    "T": "I'm the Chief Mate of the Black Nacre! You'll be working with me on this voyage, savvy?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chief Mate",
                    "T": "Perk up, sailors! It's your first day on deck, and our quartermaster will make sure you get the best preserved meat, cream, hardtack, and Dandelion Wine!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "The speaker continues to narrate the scene before you—\\n\\nThe Chief Mate appears to greet the raw recruits, dressed in ragged clothes and swaddled in bandages.\\nIt is obvious that he has just survived a fierce fight.\\nLooking around, you see most of the sailors are seriously wounded...\\nHowever, they are in high spirits, showing no signs of fear or being discouraged...\\nThe sailors gather around you, applauding the newcomers and offering welcome gifts and food."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh! So the speaker also provides detailed narration of the scene, like the scene just now — we were just welcomed onboard the Black Nacre..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So... shall we play along?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hehe, thank you, thank you everyone! We haven't had the preserved meat or hardtack here yet, but they must be tasty!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's a pity that we can't see the actors or props."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Otherwise, this could be quite immersive."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah... the attraction is called \"Three-Day Reverie,\" so are we just supposed to rely on our own powers of daydreaming?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Though, it probably does save a lot on costs... Building a real pirate ship, actually being able to sail anywhere at a moment's notice... That must be expensive..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But still! Only having a narrator is too far. We can only imagine so much!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Guess we'll have to try!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Paimon and me, that's how it's gonna be!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, Paimon will give it a try..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Narrator On Speaker",
                    "T": "As the noise dies down, a powerful-looking man appears on the bridge."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Narrator On Speaker",
                    "T": "He is dressed just like a common sailor, save for the ragged tricorne on his head. His left hand is missing, replaced by a rusty hook."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Chief Mate",
                    "T": "Attention on deck! Captain Will's arrived!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Captain Will",
                    "T": "The time is now, me hearties! Get to your positions, double check your weapons and our supplies, and prepare the ship! Get ready to weigh anchor!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Whoa! The Captain is here. He sounds so calm... and reliable!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Captain Will",
                    "T": "The treasure isn't far now, lads! The final leg of the voyage is by far the most important!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Captain Will",
                    "T": "Our wounded comrades, drowned supplies, lost Dusk Birds, and even the casks of rum we scrimped and saved for... the price we paid will not have been in vain!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Captain Will",
                    "T": "As long as we find the legendary treasure, we can appease the Kraken before the deadline! Never again must we seek dishonest merchants to plunder for pocket change!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Captain Will",
                    "T": "So give it your all, you scurvy seadogs! Do it so our town may know peace, and our friends and family need no longer fear tyranny and toil! Full speed ahead!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sailor",
                    "T": "Treasure! Treasure! Full speed ahead! For peace!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Narrator On Speaker",
                    "T": "Having welcomed powerful new recruits aboard, the Black Nacre prepares to weigh anchor and set sail for the treasure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oooh, the speaker really set the scene! The goal of these pirates is really different from what Paimon imagined... Paimon's curious what happens next!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "The speaker said we can ride the Choo-Choo Cart to continue the play... Paimon likes this pace!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Anchors aweigh, {NICKNAME}!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
